You better get it.
Yes, sis.

00:42.083 --> 00:43.251
Yes, yes, yes, yes, yes.

00:43.334 --> 00:45.128
A little sprinkle of that,
a dash of this.

00:45.211 --> 00:46.755
That makes a perfect soup,
honey.

00:46.838 --> 00:49.966
