02:06.543 --> 02:08.461
You're gonna have to
forgive me eventually.

02:09.712 --> 02:11.965
You threatened to take
my son away from me.

02:12.048 --> 02:14.134
I'm trying to keep
our family together.

02:15.844 --> 02:17.053
Andre, I've been thinking.

02:17.137 --> 02:18.972
We shouldn't get married
next week.

02:19.055 --> 02:20.431
