this wedding.

02:20.515 --> 02:21.683
I can't think straight.

02:21.766 --> 02:22.934
I get it.

02:23.017 --> 02:25.061
Lots of change recently,
you're overwhelmed...

02:26.229 --> 02:27.397
That's why I got you
an assistant.

02:27.981 --> 02:29.149
Courtney.

02:30.775 --> 02:33.570
Courtney is gonna help you out
with whatever you need:

02:33.653 --> 02:37.073
driving you around, errands,
wedding planning,

02:37.657 --> 02:38.908
changing diapers...

02:39.868 --> 02:41.578
24/7.

02:41.661 --> 02:44.205
You're busy,
and you're stressed...

02:45.206 --> 02:46.833
And I'll feel better
knowing that you're safe.

02:46.916 --> 02:48.376
Just think of Courtney
as an extra set

02:48.459 --> 02:49.711
of eyes and hands...

02:50.795 --> 02:52.046
whenever you need.

02:52.463 --> 02:53.548
You're right.

02:55.466 --> 02:58.845
Walker has his six-month
appointment this afternoon.

02:58.928 --> 03:00.388
So we're gonna have to leave
here around noon.

03:00.722 --> 03:01.806
Yes, ma'am.

03:03.224 --> 03:07.520
♪ ♪

03:10.106 --> 03:11.733
