to the world

03:29.417 --> 03:31.252
in a big, gigantic way,

03:31.753 --> 03:34.672
and that's why we got you here,
Destiny.

03:34.923 --> 03:36.132
You're looking for a banger?

03:36.216 --> 03:37.300
Yeah.

03:37.383 --> 03:38.593
