for other artists,

03:40.094 --> 03:41.512
but Yana's special.

03:41.846 --> 03:44.390
Uh, Lucious,
can we talk in private?

03:44.474 --> 03:46.392
-Of course.
-Oh, anything you need to say

03:46.476 --> 03:48.061
