08:06.152 --> 08:07.778
Have you lost your damn mind?

08:07.862 --> 08:08.946
What?

08:09.030 --> 08:10.531
You--this is my house.

08:10.615 --> 08:12.909
How in the hell you bitches
even get up in here?

08:12.992 --> 08:14.869
I bought you the damn house,
Carol.

08:14.952 --> 08:17.288
-I got a key, stupid.
-Is that what you're doing?

08:17.371 --> 08:19.207
You gonna throw all your money
up in my face again?

08:19.290 --> 08:20.625
Is that what you came here for?

08:20.708 --> 08:22.627
- You are out of control, Carol.
- Yeah, bitch!

08:22.710 --> 08:25.004
You damn right I am.
Now get out, both of y'all.

08:25.087 --> 08:26.088
- Get out.
- You need help!

08:26.172 --> 08:27.757
I don't need a damn thing,
bitch,

08:27.840 --> 08:29.425
but to be left alone.

08:29.509 --> 08:32.053
And you know what?
Who the hell you think you is?

08:32.136 --> 08:33.471
You ruined my life.

08:33.554 --> 08:35.765
You think I can't
do the same to yo' ass?

08:35.848 --> 08:36.933
What you mean by that?

08:37.016 --> 08:39.143
Carol, stop talking crazy.
Carol!

08:39.227 --> 08:41.020
- Carol!
- No, stop it!

08:41.103 --> 08:42.438
You are going to rehab.

08:42.522 --> 08:43.606
- Give me my joint.
- Come on. Come on.

08:43.689 --> 08:44.774
No, give me my joint.

08:44.857 --> 08:46.442
-No.
-Stop! Come on.

08:49.612 --> 08:53.324
♪ Now I know
that I done wrong ♪

08:53.950 --> 08:57.245
♪ I'm gonna keep trying,
trying, trying ♪

08:59.330 --> 09:01.874
♪ Been alone
so many times before ♪

09:02.542 --> 09:04.502
♪ I'm gonna keep biding ♪

09:04.585 --> 09:06.712
♪ ♪

09:06.796 --> 09:10.174
♪ Everybody's gonna
fall down sometime ♪

09:10.258 --> 09:12.093
♪ ♪

09:12.176 --> 09:14.303
All right, y'all, wherever
y'all trying to take me,

09:14.387 --> 09:15.721
I'm not going.

09:15.805 --> 09:17.056
