cleaned up.

09:20.184 --> 09:21.227
All right, come on, y'all.

09:21.310 --> 09:23.354
Come on.

09:23.437 --> 09:26.232
Just take me back home.
I'm good.

09:26.315 --> 09:28.568
Y'all ain't got to worry
about me no more.

09:28.651 --> 09:30.987
Y'all, I'm saying
"no" to drugs.

09:31.070 --> 09:34.365
