if you think that you are good.

09:34.448 --> 09:37.118
Mm, soon as we pull over,
you'll ditch us in five seconds

09:37.201 --> 09:38.786
to go cop you a fix, honey.

09:38.869 --> 09:40.663
-Mm-hmm.
-You need to be thinking

09:40.746 --> 09:41.914
about your kids, Carol.

09:41.998 --> 09:43.040
Girl, please.

09:43.124 --> 09:44.792
You need to be thinking
about your own damn kids.

09:44.875 --> 09:45.960
Okay.

09:46.043 --> 09:47.128
You wasn't there during

09:47.211 --> 09:49.130
Andre's bipolar breakdowns,

09:49.213 --> 09:50.715
and you damn sure wasn't there

09:50.798 --> 09:52.883
when Lucious was shunning Jamal
for being gay.

09:52.967 --> 09:55.386
Hell, you didn't even see
Hakeem learn how to walk.

09:55.469 --> 09:57.680
I don't need a recap, okay?

09:59.223 --> 10:01.684
One of the biggest regrets
of my life...

10:02.768 --> 10:04.645
not being there
to raise my boys.

10:04.729 --> 10:06.522
Mm-hmm.
Yeah, you knew

10:06.606 --> 10:08.482
what it was like
to not have a mama,

10:08.566 --> 10:11.402
and you still abandoned
your boys, you stupid bitch.

10:11.485 --> 10:14.071
So what does that make you,
stupid bitch?

10:14.280 --> 10:15.364
Huh?

10:15.448 --> 10:17.825
You want your kids to be
without their mother?

10:17.908 --> 10:20.995
Yeah, Mama leaving
changed all of us, didn't it?

10:21.078 --> 10:23.706
No one should have to grow up
without a mother.

10:25.333 --> 10:27.460
This is your fault,
not mine.

10:27.543 --> 10:28.628
Stop it.
Stop.

10:28.711 --> 10:30.796
You're always making excuses
for the girls.

10:30.880 --> 10:32.298
No!
No, you can't see them,

10:32.381 --> 10:33.633
'cause I'm their father.

10:33.716 --> 10:35.176
Renee, stay away from here.

10:35.259 --> 10:36.844
We don't want to see you
ever again.

10:36.927 --> 10:38.304
Stay away from the girls.

10:40.431 --> 10:42.099
Dad, where's Mom?

10:43.684 --> 10:45.436
Candace, go get your sisters
ready for school.

10:51.275 --> 10:53.069
Candace, where's Mama?

10:53.152 --> 10:54.528
We'll need
to get ourselves ready.

10:54.612 --> 10:55.946
I'm sure Mom will
be right back.

10:56.030 --> 10:58.866
But Mama said she was gonna
help me with me outfit!

10:58.949 --> 11:00.701
Loretha, help with Carol.

11:00.785 --> 11:02.536
You heard her, Carol.
Don't start acting up.

11:02.620 --> 11:05.373
I want Mama now!

11:05.456 --> 11:06.666
Carol, Stop it!

11:06.749 --> 11:08.376
- Get up!
- Ah! Leave me alone!

11:08.459 --> 11:10.586
Come on, Carol, let's go!

11:10.670 --> 11:12.254
Leave me alone!

11:13.964 --> 11:16.592
You are so full of it,
Candace.

11:16.676 --> 11:18.135
You are.
You lied about Mama

11:18.219 --> 11:20.262
just like you lied
about Franklin.

11:20.346 --> 11:21.847
Carol, please.

11:21.931 --> 11:23.557
Okay, I'll admit it.

11:23.641 --> 11:26.060
Sometimes the truth
is too damn hard to face.

11:26.143 --> 11:28.562
Yeah, 'cause your saditty ass
is fake.

11:28.646 --> 11:29.897
Look...

11:31.107 --> 11:32.400
I know I made a mistake
with my son.

11:32.483 --> 11:33.651
I'll admit that.

11:33.734 --> 11:37.029
Thought Cookie was crazy
for calling the cops.

11:39.865 --> 11:41.742
But that was the wake-up call
that I needed.

11:44.245 --> 11:46.539
I was blessed to have
my sisters there with me.

11:47.957 --> 11:50.209
Y'all both saved me
and Franklin,

11:50.292 --> 11:52.545
just like we're trying to save
yo' ass.

11:52.628 --> 11:53.838
Oh, I don't need no saving.

11:53.921 --> 11:55.381
Oh, yes, you do, honey.

11:55.464 --> 11:57.466
By the grace of God,
yes, you do.

11:57.550 --> 11:58.676
-Amen.
-Huh.

11:58.759 --> 12:02.221
And if you was real,
you would face that reality.

12:03.347 --> 12:06.517
♪ Oh, whoa, oh, oh ♪

12:07.435 --> 12:09.895
♪ I'm going to be saved ♪

12:14.400 --> 12:15.484
Let's see.
So...

12:15.568 --> 12:16.861
♪ See me, feel me ♪

12:16.944 --> 12:18.738
♪ Touch me, heal me ♪

12:18.821 --> 12:20.531
♪ You and I... ♪

12:20.614 --> 12:22.783
No, it needs to go...
♪ See me ♪

12:22.867 --> 12:24.785
♪ ♪

12:24.869 --> 12:26.078
Can you give us a minute?

12:27.288 --> 12:28.831
How's it going?

12:28.914 --> 12:30.708
This is what I got so far.

12:32.877 --> 12:37.214
"See me, feel me, touch me,
you and I intertwined."

12:38.883 --> 12:42.219
